==Bengali==
{{rfc|needs formatting (is it a noun? Then why isn't the definition AFTER the noun section?}}
* Muslim way of greeting someone, especially in [[South Asia]] ([[Bangladesh]], [[India]], [[Pakistan]]).

* Literally, means ''Peace''.

* Pronounced Salaam. 

* Shortened version of আসসালামু আলাইকুম (Assalamu Alaikum), which means "Peace be upon you".

